  ('optometrist-moex-00064', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為維持視網膜色素上皮細胞（retinapigmentepithelium）與神經視網膜（neuralretina）彼此附著之', '["細胞骨架（cytoskeleton）連接", "結締組織（connective tissue）", "粘性蛋白多醣（viscous proteoglycans）", "靜電力（electrostaticforces）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a07a9f0fc159", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e918d93fe3c9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00065', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列與視神經相關之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["視神經盤（opticcanal）的血液支配主要來自後睫動脈分支（branchesofposteriorciliaryarteries）", "眼眶內視神經遠端（intraorbital optic nerve; distal part）的血液支配主要來自中心網膜動脈神經內分支 （intraneuralbranchesofcentralretinalartery）", "眼眶內視神經近端（intraorbitalopticnerve;proximalpart）的血液支配主要來自軟腦膜血管與眼動脈分支 （pialvesselsandbranchesofophthalmicartery）", "顱內視神經（intracrainalopticnerve）的血液支配主要來自中大腦動脈（middlecerebralartery）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a07a9f0fc159", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e918d93fe3c9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
